--------General:--------
- '_Measures Folder' - 1 folder with subfolders in it
- 'zLookup Queries' - for fact tables
- 'zzCalendar Query' - for calendar table

- Turn off auto date/time
- Turn off refresh of fact tables if possible

- Prefix pages with TT_ for tooltip pages and hide

--------Measures:--------
- Capitalized / Normalized names
- variables with an underscore
- variables with sensible short names
- variables end with '_Result' variable then 'RETURN _Result' (makes error checking easier)
- Add basic comments if its complex

--------Calculate Columns/Tables:--------
- Avoid if possible
- Prefix with _CC / _CT to group and make obvious whats calculated
- Add basic comments if its complex

--------:--------
